# Environment overrides for the Gemma-4-E4B demo model.
#
# Model lives on NVMe (/srv/nclaw is the nclawzero data partition, set up
# by nclawzero-init-storage). Rootfs SD card is too small for a 5GB GGUF.
#
# Defaults match TYPHON's live config (Phil Lawrence demo rig):
#   MODEL_NAME=gemma-4-E4B-it-Q4_K_M.gguf
#   MODEL_DIR=/srv/nclaw/models
#
# Sources tried in order by fetch-gemma.sh:
#   1. $TYPHON_SRC = jasonperlow@192.168.207.61:/home/jasonperlow/models/gemma-4-E4B-Q4/<NAME>
#      (needs $TYPHON_PASS or pubkey auth)
#   2. $MODEL_URL (HuggingFace fallback)
#
# Operator: set ONE of TYPHON_PASS or MODEL_URL before enabling
# nclawzero-demo-gemma-fetch.service.

# TYPHON_PASS=Gumbo@Kona1b
# MODEL_URL=https://huggingface.co/unsloth/gemma-4-E4B-it-GGUF/resolve/main/gemma-4-E4B-it-Q4_K_M.gguf
